The lesson about Baraka ummu Ayman r.a.

Today I learned the life of the Baraka ummu Ayman r.a. She was with the Prophet Muhammad (sollalohu alayhi vasallam) in her entira life. She was as a mother to him s.a.v.

Data Structures in Python

Our professor showed us various types of data structures in Python programming language.
Actually, they are:
- Lists,
- Dictionaries,
- Arrays, linked arrays
- Trees and graphs
